1. *Bolest* je stanje u kojem se telo bori protiv infekcije. (Disease is a state in which the body fights against infection.)

2. Postoje različite vrste *bolesti*, posebno one koje su vezane za bolesti krvi. (There are various types of diseases, especially those related to blood diseases.)

3. U nekim slučajevima, veoma suštinska *bolest* može biti izlečena lekovima. (In some cases, a very fundamental disease can be cured by medicine.)

4. *Bolest* je česta pojava kod ljudi koji žive u zagušenim, zagađenim mestima. (Disease is a common occurrence in people living in congested, polluted places.)

5. *Bolest* može biti uzrokovana genetskim predispozicijama ili nepravilnom ishranom. (Disease can be caused by genetic predisposition or improper nutrition.)